http://wikiceleb.com/egypt-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-01-23 22:17:25";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-01-23 16:32:25";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:27:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=634";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"644";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-12-25 23:16:42";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-12-25 17:31:42";s:12:"post_content";s:14653:"<p style="text-align: justify;">The FIFA World Cup is the most prestigious and respectable tournament in the world football and with<a href="http://wikiceleb.com/russia-host-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Russiaâ€™s</a> 2018 tournament edition almost at our doorstep, many strikers, wingers or many players will be seeking to show their capabilities and to write their names in the world football. Talking about the strikers and wingers, they are in the eye of football fans because they are more responsible for scoring goals. Forwards in the football team are the players who play closest to the opposing teamâ€™s goal and are therefore score more goal than other teammates. And a winger is an attacking player who is responsible to beat opposing full-backs, crosses from a wide position with their speed, skill, and vision. Here are 11 of the best strikers/wingers in the world.</p>
11.Â <strong>Sadio Mane</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-646" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sadio-mane-1-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="358" />

Full Name: Sadio Mane

Birth Date: 10 April 1992

Age: 25

Nation: <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/senegal-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Senegal</a>

Current Club: Liverpool FC
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sadio Mane is the most loved footballer by Liverpool fans where he made an immediate impact for English premier league side Liverpool FC after the transfer from Southampton. His pace and creativity from wings is a thing to watch. His national side Senegal from South Africa was qualified after many years so Mane is the main man to lead his nation in upcoming FIFA world cup. He has 46 international caps for Senegal with 13 goals.</p>
10.<strong>Raheem Sterling</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-647" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Raheem-Shaquille-Sterling-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="531" height="354" />

Full Name: Raheem Shaquille Sterling

Birth Date: 8 December 1994

Age: 23

Nation:<a href="http://wikiceleb.com/england-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> England</a>

Current Club: Manchester City
<p style="text-align: justify;">Raheem Sterling was regarded as the most talented young player in England where he is slowly proving his worth this season in English premier league for Manchester City under Pep Guardiola. He is scoring many goals from the wing and providing assists. So he will be the main man to lead the attack from the wing for England in upcoming FIFA world cup. His pace and vision will make attacking side of England football team more vulnerable in FIFA world cup. He has 35 international caps for England with 2 goals in all competition.</p>
9.<strong>Thomas Muller</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-648" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/mullar-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="410" />

Full Name: Thomas Muller

Birth Date: 13 September 1989

Age: 28

Nation: <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/germany-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Germany</a>

Current Club: FC Bayern Munich
<p style="text-align: justify;">Thomas Muller was the main attacker for his national side Germany in previous FIFA world cup held in Brazil where he was successful in many games leading his team to win the competition. He scored many goals for Germany. Likewise in this FIFA world cup also Muller has a responsibility to take care of frontline for his side Germany and will be the player to watch this time. He will play central forward or false 9 for Germany in upcoming FIFA world cup. He has 89 international caps with 37 goals for Germany.</p>
8.<strong>Mohamed Salah Ghaly</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-649" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/salah-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="544" height="362" />

Full Name: Mohamed Salah Ghaly

Birth Date: 15 JuneÂ 1992

Age: 25

Nation: <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/egypt-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Egypt</a>

Current Club: Liverpool FC
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Â </strong>In 2017/18 season, Mohamed Salah was the man in a form where heÂ has found the net in almost games for English premier league club Liverpool FC. He captains his national side <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/egypt-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Egypt</a> who is qualified for FIFA world cup for the first time in many decades. His goals in qualifying round were vital for <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/egypt-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Egypt</a> to qualify for FIFA world cup. He is capable of playing winger and second striker. As his sides were qualified after a long time he has a huge responsibility to carry his team like he did in qualifying round. For <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/egypt-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Egypt</a>, he has 56 international caps with overall 32 goals in all competitions.</p>
7.<strong>Paulo Dybala</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-650" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/dybala-1-300x168.jpg" alt="" width="543" height="304" />

<strong>Â </strong>

Full Name: Paulo Bruno Exequiel Dybala

