Age: 24

Nation: <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a>

Current Club: Juventus
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Â </strong>Paulo Dybala also called â€œNext Messiâ€ is a central forward player who has the capability to play as winger, second striker or even no.10 positions. Due to his dribbling, visions and goal scoring capacity, he is called second Messi of <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a>. Although he has not featured most for <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a> as he is young but due to his current development and form he is surely going to play FIFA world cup with the likes of other forwards like Messi, Icardi, Di-Maria, Aguero, etc. He has only 12 international caps for <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a> and has not found goal yet but we will see his goals and assist more in upcoming FIFA world cup.</p>
<strong>Â </strong>6.<strong>Mario Mandzukic</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-651" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/mario-manduketch-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="544" height="361" />

Full Name: Mario Mandzukic

Birth Date: 21 May 1986

Age: 31

Nation: <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/croatia-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Croatia</a>

Current Club: Juventus
<p style="text-align: justify;">Mario Mandzukic is a type of player where he can play in any position up front. He has played striker role, winger and central forward role. He has offered dynamics for his club Juventus by his vision and goal scoring capability. He is a huge boost for his national side <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/croatia-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Croatia</a> where he will play with other skilled players like Modric, Kovacic, etc. So for FIFA world cup, he will have a huge role in the front line to score a goal for <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/croatia-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Croatia</a>. He has 81 international caps for <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/croatia-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Croatia</a> with 30 goals in all competition.</p>
5.<strong>Eden Hazard</strong>

