<p style="text-align: justify;">One of the best forward in English Premier League, Hazard is regarded as a wizard of skills, vision and goals after Leo Messi. He has been linked with Spanish giant Real Madrid many times. Availability of Hazard makes <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/belgium-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Belgium</a> squad stronger in up front with Lukaku and Mertens. In front line, he will offer more creativity and goals which we will see in upcoming FIFA world cup. For his national side <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/belgium-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Belgium</a> he has 82 international caps with 21 goals.</p>
