<p style="text-align: justify;">Arguably one of the most skilled and talented player in the world, Messi captains his national side <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a> in FIFA world cup. He is the main man for his Spanish team FC Barcelona who brings revolution in world football. He has helped his club to win many trophies and trebles several times. In previous FIFA world cup also Messi was the main man to lead <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a> up to finals of FIFA world cup although they lost. In upcoming FIFA world cup, Messi will be one of the hot topics among football players alongside Cristiano Ronaldo. He has 123 international caps with 61 goals.</p>
